<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich Thannhauser und Peter Baiersdorfer</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er derzeit niemanden als Diener einstellt.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_157" id="78v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_157_r1l22"><expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Tanhawſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>payrſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_157_r1l23"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Tanhawſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>payrſtorff<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l24">Jr vns <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenen vnd etwıeuıl <expan>geſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt eẅch <expan>brınge<ex>n</ex></expan> wolt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l25">etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd danken eẅch des mıt fleıſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l26">Vnd laſſen eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ vnſer ſach alſo geſtalt ıſt daʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l27">ʒu dıſer ʒeit niht mer dıener bedürffen . wurden wır aber der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l28">leẅt <expan>bedurff<ex>en</ex></expan> So <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darauf bedacht ſein . Denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_157_r1l29">wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> georij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_157" id="78v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Tanhaws<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Payrstorff<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Tanhaws<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>Payrstorff<ex>er,</ex></expan>
                        als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir uns
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienen und etwievil
                                <expan>gesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit ewch
                            <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan> wolt etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und danken ewch des mit fleiss und lassen ewch
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz unser sach also gestalt ist, daz wir
                        zu diser zeit niht mer diener bedürffen. Wurden wir aber der lewt
                                <expan>bedurff<ex>en,</ex></expan> so <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darauf bedacht sein. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Georii. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
